softIocPVA \- Minimal EPICS IOC for tests and demos
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.nf 
.fam C
\fBsoftIocPVA\fP [\fB\-D\fP softIoc.dbd] [\fB\-h\fP] [\fB\-S\fP] [\fB\-a\fP \fIascf\fP]
      [\fB\-m\fP \fImacro=value,macro2=value2\fP] [\fB\-d\fP file.db]
